value.string: SELECT Type, count(*) as total FROM [Fleet Management] WHERE Type is not null GROUP BY Type
SELECT VehicleModel, count(*) as total FROM [Fleet Management] WHERE VehicleModel is not null GROUP BY VehicleModel
select [Type of Permit],count(*) as total from [Fleet Management] where [Type of Permit] is not null Group By [Type of Permit]
select VehicleNumber , [PUC Expiry date] date from [Fleet Management]
select VehicleNumber ,  [Insurance Due Date] from [Fleet Management]
Trip start time and End time
select VehicleNumber, [Pick-up date], [Delivery date], Driver from [Fleet Management]where Driver<>''
select VehicleNumber, Source, Destination, Driver from [Fleet Management]where Driver<>''
PUC Expired vehicle more than 6 months
SELECT VehicleNumber,[PUC Expiry date] FROM [Fleet Management]WHERE CONVERT(datetime, [PUC Expiry date], 103) <= dateadd(month, -6, getdate())
SELECT VehicleNumber,[Registration Date] FROM [Fleet Management]WHERE CONVERT(datetime, [Registration Date], 103) <= dateadd(year, -14, getdate())
SELECT VehicleNumber,[Insurance Due Date] FROM [Fleet Management]WHERE CONVERT(datetime, [Insurance Due Date], 103) <= dateadd(year, -4, getdate())
